{"tid":851697,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人行降準1% 專家：發出強烈訊號來穩定股市","createTime":"2018-10-07T10:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T18:57:43.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9c29a707c9ebf53ff0ba1e42e56d30d42ef370a1","tid":851697,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"2018-10-07 16:03&nbsp;聯合報 記者杜宗熹╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行今天中午宣布，自10月15日起調降準備率1個百分點，專家認為，大陸「十一」黃金周期間，海外市場各國的股票市場，均出現了不同程度的下跌，人行此時降準，釋放出強烈的穩定市場訊號。當然，市場是否買賬，還要等到明天股匯市開市才能再看結果。<br />\n澎湃新聞網報導，大陸金融分析師簡容指出，香港恆生指數創下8個月來的最大單週跌幅，上週三港股沽空比率一度高達18%，是29個月來的新高。雖然由於假期因素，大陸境內市場暫時躲過了海外市場調整外溢性影響，但節後開市能否穩住，存在較高的不確定性。"},{"pid":"fc6f7dab5ab9608c7754006bb93a41450332f32a","tid":851697,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"月中先有熱錢流入"},{"pid":"a9012f6ece30fbb4b2fde3afcd107d11a49bd202","tid":851697,"uid":52595,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"310a999a390b91fe654447bea3671011d66953ef","tid":851697,"uid":197163,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"聽日實上返27000"},{"pid":"8a2a0ba9139cefb698d3a8d805d264f441ac5c88","tid":851697,"uid":62067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"穩定就唔洗降準，我明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5776bd29accd6d1bbb0c1b30c90f7438d0939d","tid":851697,"uid":162526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a2a0ba9139cefb698d3a8d805d264f441ac5c88","tid":851697,"uid":62067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"穩定就唔洗降準，我明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"30000話穩到26000，穩左幾次，有冇人會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\